      "csl:pageColumn": "168,2",
      "rdf:value": "<L>29396<pc>168,2<k1>il<k2>il<e>1\r\n<s>il</s> ¦ <ab>cl.</ab> 6. <ab>P.</ab> <s>ilati</s> (<s>iyela</s>, <s>elizyati</s>, <s>ElIt</s>, <s>elitum</s>, <ls>Dhātup. xxviii, 65</ls>) to come, <ls>Hariv.</ls>; <ls>VP.</ls>;\r\n<div n=\"to\"/>to send, cast, <ls>L.</ls>;\r\n<div n=\"to\"/>to sleep, <ls>L.</ls> : <ab>cl.</ab> 10. <ab>P.</ab> <s>ilayati</s> (<ab>Impv.</ab> 2. <ab>pl.</ab> <s>ila/yatA</s>, <ls>AV. i, 17, 4</ls>) or <s>elayati</s> (<ls>Pāṇ. iii, 1, 51</ls>) <ab>aor.</ab> <s>Elilat</s> or <s>ElayIt</s>, to keep still, not to move;\r\n<div n=\"to\"/>to become quiet, <ls>AV.</ls>; <ls>TS.</ls>; <ls>ŚBr.</ls> &c.;\r\n<div n=\"vp\"/> <info westergaard=\"ila,28.65,06.0064\"/><info whitneyroots=\"il,9\"/><info verb=\"genuineroot\" cp=\"6P,10P\"/>\r\n<LEND>"
    },
